5:
What is this place? Everyone looks like 
me…
16:
Travelers from afar. 
We mean you no harm.
19:
Wait, are you—he is! He really is!
King Whitetail!
21:
King Whitetail?! But he was—
Oh, oh my goodness, I can't believe it! 
The king has returned! I'm—*sniffle*—
I'm sho glad you're alibveee!
23:
Our king, our hope!
Quick, get the others!
28:
CALLING ALL CATFOOOLK!
THE KING HAS RETUUURNED!
GODKING WHITETAIL LIIIVES!
31:
He's got a royal escort too!
I've never seen anyone like them!
38:
Dude, what's all the racket? There's no 
way it could REALLY be King Whitetail... 
or is there?
41:
Would you cut out the King Whitetail 
crap already? I've never even heard of 
the guy!
43: I can't believe I lived to see this day…
47:
Please, calm down.
We just arrived and would appreciate 
if someone could explain where we are.
59:
All right, all right, give the poor dudes 
some room to breathe! I'd be happy 
to answer any questions!
63:
I'm Claudius, by the way! Pretty much 
everyone calls me Claw, though. Like 
to keep it short and sweet, y'know?
66:
I don't care who YOU are, I just 
wanna know what's goin' on here!
71:
Claw, do you know of any old ruins in 
the area? We're looking for—
79:
At a time like this? C'mon man, 
couldn't they have waited a few 
minutes?
82:
Your highness! Now that you've 
returned, we can send those mangy 
mutts packing for once and for all!
84:
Mutts? Must be those dog-like 
beastfolk from before. What are you 
tryin' to rope us into?
88: No time to ask now! Let's go, Nimbus!
92:
Fine, FINE! But I better get a DAMN 
GOOD explanation for all this later!
